laboratory_examinations.findings: MIXED BACTERIAL FLORA (>= 3 COLONY TYPES), CONSISTENT WITH SKIN AND/OR GENITAL CONTAMINATION. 8.0 mg/dL (reference range: 8.4 - 10.3 mg/dL)

Bowel gas pattern is non-specific with air in mildly distended loops of small bowel to 4.3cm. A small amount of air in the rectum. Contrast from the CT scan is seen in the ascending colon. No free air noted.
